Our commitment to sustainability includes helping you find ways to work smarter and faster, while improving your bottom line and the environment. Since our earliest days, we have strived to find ways to make the office more sustainable. We invented technology to enable two-side copying and introduced the first recycled grade of cut sheet paper. The use of both has become second nature for many. Here are tips using the latest product features and functionalities to make your office more sustainable. Steps to a more sustainable office This article was published in partnership with Altron Bytes Document Solutions.